          "q": "New HR Manager at Flipkart: Ops attrition spike. First move in 60 mins?",
          "explain_this": "Triage: define impact, owner, timeline, minimum facts.",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "Define scope + pull 3 key data points",
              "feedback": "You frame impact → faster alignment."
            },
            {
              "text": "Broadcast a generic policy reminder",
