            },
            {
              "text": "Start a long survey immediately",
              "feedback": "You add delay → urgency compounds."
            },
            {
              "text": "Ask teams to handle it locally",
              "feedback": "You lose visibility → actions fragment."
            }
          ],
          "correct_index": 0
        },
        {
          "q_id": "SC01_Q02",
          "q": "Early signals conflict. What’s the safest next step?",
          "explain_this": "Containment: reduce harm now while verifying facts.",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "Separate facts vs claims; list gaps",
              "feedback": "You stay neutral → path to proof opens."
            },
            {
              "text": "Assume senior version is true",
              "feedback": "You bias early → decisions get challenged."
            },
            {
              "text": "Wait for perfect information",
              "feedback": "You delay action → risk grows."
            },
